Chronicle — Durable Streams protocol server on Redis 8

Portions of this software (the storage contract in store/, protocol header
constants, and handler structure) are derived from the Durable Streams
reference Caddy plugin:

  https://github.com/durable-streams/durable-streams (packages/caddy-plugin)
